To run the slcsp code with the input files provided in the adhoc github repo:
- create a virtualenv using python 3.6.0-3.6.5 and move the zip directory into it:
virtualenv -p python3 venv
mv slscp_problem-master venv/

- activate the virtualenv and install the required packages
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

To run the slcsp calculation code:
python slcsp_calc.py

output slcsp.zip file in the working directory will have the annotated slcsp rates

To run the tests:
pytest --verbose
